snippet.title: Adventure Ages | Behind The Ages, Part 2 | Launches Feb 1st on the App Store and Google Play!
snippet.description:
Transport Behind The Ages on AdVenture Ages with Liam, Emma, Augusto, and Lindsay and learn more about what went into creating our new game.
 
They jam on:
➡ most exciting features
➡ developing remotely
➡ similarities with AdVenture Communist
➡ player participation

Download AdVenture Ages on February 1st: bit.ly/AgesYTDL

Continue transporting behind the ages here:
Facebook: http://bit.ly/AdAgesFB
Twitter: http://bit.ly/AdAgesTW
Instagram: http://bit.ly/AdAgesIG
Reddit: http://bit.ly/AdAgesRI
